Math:Bezier::Convert - Convert cubic and quadratic bezier each other.

Install:

  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make install

There isn't test scripts yet.  Sample script with Tk is in ./samples 
directory, instead.
See perldoc Math:Bezier::Convert for further information.

Yasuhiro Sasama (ySas), <ysas@nmt.ne.jp>